+    - `vLLM`: `longbench_multifieldqa_en`
+    - `SGLang`: `longbench_multifieldqa_en`, `longbench_2wikimqa`, `longbench_qasper`, `longbench_triviaqa`, `longbench_v2`, `leval_Generation_multidoc_qa`
+  - Optional after schema repair:
+    - `sharegpt_real`, `random_control`, `gsm8k_custom`, `gsp_chunk_jitter`
+- Compared systems:
+  - `vLLM` versus `SGLang`
+  - case families: `chunk/nochunk`, `eplb/noeplb`
+- Metrics:
+  - `U1 = whole_model_cv_all_weighted`
+    - For step `t`, sum routed tokens over all MoE layers by rank.
+    - Let `p_t(r) = c_t(r) / sum_r c_t(r)`.
+    - `cv_t = std_r(p_t(r)) / mean_r(p_t(r))`.
+    - Weighted mean over steps using total routed tokens at step `t`.
+  - `U2 = whole_model_cv_prefill_weighted`
